headline: Is Humana (HUM) Offering Value After DCF And P/E Suggest Upside Potential
summary: If you are wondering whether Humana's current share price still reflects good value, it helps to step back and look at what the recent returns and fundamentals are actually telling you. Humana's stock last closed at US$275.80, with returns of 6.5% over the past week, 7.0% over the past month, 4.3% year to date, 4.7% over the past year, a 40.8% decline over three years, and a 31.7% decline over five years. Taken together, these figures give a mixed picture of recent momentum and longer term...
